issue.title: Morph requires experimental nix-commands to be enabled
issue.body:
Very recently nix in nixos-unstable has been upgrade to 2.4. Now I am forced to enable the nix-command, which is deemed experimental.

```
❯ morph deploy default.nix switch
error: experimental Nix feature 'nix-command' is disabled; use '--extra-experimental-features nix-command' to override
```

comment.body: The fix is included in morph 1.7.0, which is not in 21.11, but is in unstable (and thus the upcoming 22.05). Sorry for the inconvenience. :)
